                       AND No structural errors (Check 5, 6)
                       AND Check 7 passes
                       → fixes must be []

  retry                Any CRITICAL missing workflow
                       OR any CRITICAL phantom
                       OR 3+ minor missing
                       OR 3+ minor phantoms
                       OR any structural error (wrong conditional, generic on_success)
                       OR Check 7 failure
